roomTypes.description: The Presidential Nirvana Suite is luxurious and expansive with 260 sq mt area boasting two bedrooms, a spacious living area, dining room overlooking outdoor infinity pool with fully equipped service pantry, a comfortable lounge area and a separate study in both the bedrooms. State-of-the-art amenities include three LCD televisions, Comp Basic Wifi Upto 4 devices and a well designed work space. The suite is designed with taste and elegance, keeping in mind the highest standards of comfort for our guests. Its exquisite interiors and impeccable service combine to make it the most graceful and elegant suite in the hotel. The Presidential Suite is ideal for leisurely holidays to explore the cultural wonders of Surajkund and Delhi. The warm color tones, handpicked artwork and furnishings ensure that even the busiest of business trips turn into an experience of sheer luxury. The living room is well furnished and features designer furniture and artifacts, LCD television and comfortable sofas. Adjoining the room is a private terrace overlooking the Central Courtyard showcasing the intricate water fountains. The splendid bathroom features his and her wash basin, a separate enclosed steam and shower panel, a bathtub and powder room. The suite also features a lavish dressing area, which includes a walk-in closet with a large luggage rack and an in-room safe. The Presidential Suite occupants have their very own dedicated butler, who will cater to the guest best pole and minute needs during the stay.
